  "title": "Student Care Teacher (Serangoon) - O level / A level / ITE",
  "description": "<p><strong>Candidate must be available to commence employment on 19 February.</strong><br /><strong></strong><br />Job Description</p><p>1) Provide academic guidance, care and supervision to children in their homework, spelling and centre programmes</p><p>2) Meet educational goals and enrolment targets of Learning Studio Educare</p><p>Job Requirements</p><p>1) Minimum 3 GCE ‘O’ levels subject passes; English inclusive or Higher NITEC Certificate</p><p>2) Diploma in Community and Social Service / Early Childhood / Education / Healthcare or WSQ Certificate in Student Care is an added advantage</p><p>3) Keen passion to mentor, guide and supervise children in MOE Primary Schools as a long-term commitment goal in your career</p><p>4) Capable of working proactively in a dynamic environment</p><p>5) Familiarity with the local educational system and local culture is an added advantage<br /></p><p></p><p>Part-time hours: 30-40 per week</p><p>Job Types: Part-time or Full-time, Permanent, Contract<br /></p><p>Salary: $1,500.00 - $2,100.00 per month</p><p>Benefits:</p><ul><li>Additional leave</li><li>Flexible schedule</li><li>Professional development</li></ul><p>Schedule:</p><ul><li>Day shift</li><li>Monday to Friday</li></ul><p>Supplemental Pay:</p><ul><li>Performance bonus</li><li>Retention bonus</li></ul>",
